I think its time move the Spark Load out of the Doris' core.
The compatibility issue of Spark and other Hadoop related components is terrible and it is not suitable to be in Doris' core code any more.

> why add a New file scan node? the file scan node is not public to our user, you can add your code in the file scan node

We are refactoring the whole scan node framework. all scan node will be derived from `VScanNode`.
And this is a bypass, after all is done, the old scan node will be removed.
